{"tid":2314734,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"估唔到JO1係日本被J家打壓到仆街，都有得上MAMA表演","createTime":"2020-12-06T17:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T08:03:51.000Z","uid":152123,"like":14,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e09b8b7e246c294bf60214d79c87eebb37be2eb3","tid":2314734,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"恭喜JO1有得上MAMA表演！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TA5NZKswrWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTA5NZKswrWw&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2v3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=633e2c6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TA5NZKswrWw</a><br />\n<br />\n介紹翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢隊係日本produce101組合<br />\n出道一年來，有傳被J家打壓<br />\n好多大節目都冇得上，包括Music Station同紅白等等<br />\n今年有得上FNS已經好好<br />\n估唔到有得係MAMA上面表演兩首歌<br />\n真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFNS:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wtSNISAoXLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwtSNISAoXLQ&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2v3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=e419b433\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wtSNISAoXLQ</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢地唔夠泡菜仔咁靚仔<br />\n但全部都係完全素人出身<br />\n即係唔係研究生背景，而係自己走去報名<br />\n睇住佢哋參加比賽個陣<del>又柒又廢</del><br />\n依家慢慢磨煉到實力 唱得跳得有台型<br />\n希望大家畀次機會佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ibjLhgmHjM4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FibjLhgmHjM4&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2v3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=e7cb51f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ibjLhgmHjM4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0JI488RLqJw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0JI488RLqJw&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2v3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=620b36a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0JI488RLqJw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/714AOK2UBfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F714AOK2UBfo&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2v3PLjr3aI%2B